               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Wǝddāse Māryām “Praise of Mary” (fols. 3ra-18rb)
 II) Mawāśǝʾt
                     za-falāsǝyān, Antiphonary for the hermits (fols. 19ra-22rb) 
 III) Ṣalota
                     kidān za-śalastu gizeyāt “Covenant of the three hours”, introductory prayer in
                     ʾararay-mode (fol. 22va-vb)(MQ, Śǝrʿāta qǝddāse, ch. III, § 174) 
 IV)
                     Mǝʿrāf, The Common of the Office (fols. 23ra-36vb)
 IV-1) Wāzemā, The
                     Office of Vigils (fols. 23ra-26va) 
 IV-2) Kǝśtat za-ʾaryām, The festive
                     Office (fols. 26vb-36vb) 
 V) Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary (for the feasts of the
                     year) (fols. 38ra-120v)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
